title: Hour 2 - Jeff Passan and Michael Phelps (07-29-20)
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Jeff Passan and Michael Phelps (07-29-20)
description:
Jeff Passan talks to Dan about Joe Kelly. Jeff says it would be hard to prove the intent of Joe Kelly in throwing the ball at the head of an Houston Astros player. Jeff says that Joe Kelly is known as a wild pitcher anyways. Michael Phelps tells Dan what life is like after swimming and how he deals with depression.
